2/?page_id=60',0,'page','',0),(61,1,'2017-04-27 18:24:27','2017-04-27 18:24:27','What is Ticket Rush?\r\nTicket Rush is one of the leading event ticketing solution I the UAE, GCC and the middle east.\r\n\r\nHow does Ticket Rush work?\r\nJust log in to our website, selecy your event ticket, purchace, print and enjoy the show .\r\n\r\nWhy should I use Ticket Rush?\r\nLicensed and reliable ticketing solution\r\nYou get the tickets right away.\r\nThe tickets can be printed when you wish and you don\'t need to be afraid of misplacing them.\r\nIf you buy more than one ticket in your order, you can send the PDF to the others in your party .\r\nHow will I get my tickets?\r\nAn e-mail will sed to you with PDF attachment that you can open and print.\r\n\r\nNote: If you have purchased more than one ticket in your order, you will need to print all pages, as each page (ticket) has its own barcode.\r\n\r\nAre the tickets valid at the venue?\r\nA printed ticket is the same as fiscal ticket with barcode and information that allows you to enter the event venue.\r\n\r\nWhat happens if I print the ticket more than once or make a copy of it?\r\nOnly the first scan of the barcode on the ticket will grant entry.\r\n\r\nIf there are multiple copies of the same ticket, the scanner at the door will tell you that the ticket has already been scanned and you will not gain entry. The buyer\'s name is listed on the ticket.\r\n\r\nWhy is Tickets are not offered for all events?\r\nThe promoter / organizer decides if tickets can purchased and printed online otherwise tickets will be delivered to your doorsteps or collected at the venue door.\r\n\r\nWhat happens if I can\'t print the tickets?\r\nMake sure you have Adobe Acrobat Reader 4,0 (free) or later.\r\nMake sure the printer is turned on and working correctly.\r\nStill can\'t print your tickets? Contact us for help.\r\nWhat happens if ...?\r\nIf I don\'t receive the e-mail with my tickets\r\n\r\nFirst try checking your \"junk\" or \"spam\" mail folder if you have one. You can always contact us for help.\r\n\r\nRemember, you can always find your tickets under My Account. If you haven\'t received the tickets by e-mail, click My Account where you can log in and find and download your tickets under \"Order history\".\r\n\r\nWhat if my tickets are stolen?\r\nContact us for assistance.\r\n\r\nWhat if I don\'t receive my e-mail with the ticket?\r\nIf you don\'t receive an e-mail with your tickets attached you can always download and view your tickets under \"My Account\". First go to My Account and log in. Then click on the link to view your order history. On this page you can see an overview of all your orders. Click on \"Show tickets\" next to the order in question to open the PDF with the tickets.\r\n\r\nKindly note that you can contact us at any timr by sending us an-email or calling us direct.','FAQs','','inherit','closed','closed','','60-revision-v1','','','2017-04-27 18:24:27','2017-04-27 18:24:27','',60,'http://www.tktrush.com/tkt2/2017/04/27/60-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(62,1,'2017-04-27 18:25:13','2017-04-27 18:25:13',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','62','','','2017-04-27 18:34:45','2017-04-27 18:34:45','',0,'http://www.tktrush.com/tkt2/?p=62',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(63,1,'2017-04-27 18:25:13','2017-04-27 18:25:13',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','63','','','2017-04-27 18:34:45','2017-04-27 18:34:45','',0,'http://www.tktrush.com/tkt2/?p=63',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(64,1,'2017-04-27 18:27:54','2017-04-27 18:27:54','<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"background: #fff;\">\r\n<td style=\"padding: 10px; background: #fff;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"90\">\r\n<div a